      <title>欧洲央行预计从六月开始每季度降息一次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ecb-seen-cutting-interest-rates-once-a-quarter-starting-in-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社调查的经济学家表示，欧洲央行将于 6 月开始稳步渐进的降息，至少持续到明年年底。]]></description>
